text: == Events == * April 11 – Empress Zoe of Byzantium marries her chamberlain and elevates him to the throne of the Eastern Roman Empire as Michael IV. * Free County becomes subject to the Holy Roman Empire. == Births == * September 3 – Emperor Go-Sanjō of Japan (d. 1073) == Deaths == * November - King Malcolm II of Scotland, Scottish royal (b. 954) * Fulbert de Falaise, Norman Tanner (weaver) and businessman (b. c. 973)
